title: IAA Tonight | Is Pete Carroll Being a Hypocrite?
description: Seahawks coach Pete Carroll had some interesting comments about Russell Wilson on Wednesday after defeating his former QB on Monday night. Brandon Marshall used to play for the Seahawks and was not pleased with Carroll's comments.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Brandon MArshall, Omar Kelly, LeSean Mccoy)
